oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Group of female students with plaque
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A group of students holding a plaque in front of Monohan Hall. The students' names are written on the back of the photograph. Sandra Vaughn and Jo Hendricks are holding the award.
Front row, left to right: Sandra Vaughn, Jo Hendricks. Back row: Patricia Hawk, Susan Massey, Becky Brown, and D.J. White.
